headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Free Vehicle Giveaway: The Lampadati Tropos Rallye
content:
Few cars are as comfortable on tarmac as they are climbing up a mud-slicked cliff face, weaving between tree branches and boulders - the Lampadati Tropos Rallye is one such vehicle.

All players can claim a free Tropos Rallye from Southern San Andreas Super Autos any time this week between April 8th and April 14th, 2021.
